OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNursery school apologises  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor pupil discrimination   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The mother of a girl with Down's       
OL,6, syndrome who was discriminated against 
OL,7, by her former nursery school has said  
OL,8, its apology will never be enough.      
OL,10,FMichelle and Alan Cummins, whose       
OL,11,Fdaughter Amelie attended Trinity       
OL,12,FNursery School in Bangor, County Down, 
OL,13,Fbrought a case against the school.     
OL,15,FIt came after they were told Amelie,   
OL,16,Fwho is now five, would have to start 15
OL,17,Fminutes later than other children.     
OL,19,FThe school settled the case and        
OL,20,Fapologised to the Cummins family.      
